title: UFYB 111: Listener Q&A - Work + Self-Regard
itunes:title: Listener Q&A - Work + Self-Regard
description:
I’m answering work and self-worth related questions today, and I’ve seen a link across almost all the questions I’ve received. You might think these questions don’t relate to your specific circumstance if it’s not something you’re dealing with, but I’m sure you’ll find a common thread in your own life when you listen to my answers.

Get full show notes and more information here: http://unfuckyourbrain.com/111
